WEBVTT

00:00:01.208 --> 00:00:03.258
Hey, Dad, I'm over here!

00:00:07.548 --> 00:00:10.108
- Does he visit often?
- Not really. Not anymore.

00:00:10.178 --> 00:00:11.578
What can you do?

00:00:19.988 --> 00:00:22.048
Can I get some ice cream, Grandpa?

00:00:22.128 --> 00:00:23.918
Why not? You're a good girl.

00:00:24.498 --> 00:00:25.158
Hello.

00:00:41.608 --> 00:00:42.668
Christ.

